Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.45,0:02:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}{\fs45\shad3\4a&H00&}第一话 落败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别给自己太大压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.90,0:03:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不会放弃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2019年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高智能方程式 世界冠军赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终战 澳大利亚站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪亮的车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正慢慢驶向火热的战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在说「我是王者」似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着闪闪金光的车身\N领先前头的是杰奇·古德利安的克洛伊兹雪铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了这场车赛就可以达成他多年来的冠军梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.20,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是这部可怕跑车的设计者法兰兹·海尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭着自己的驾驶技术 也紧握方向盘 挤到前列来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排列第三的是光荣的11冠军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在开幕后连胜几站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.50,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是到了现在他已经完全被雪铁军团压制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入了即使赢了这场比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.20,0:03:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要古德利安保持在前三名就无法反败为胜的苦境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是否有办法创造第三次奇迹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四位的是葵车队的布里德·加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都能给人惊奇表现的车场上的风云人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着是华丽飞驰的贵公子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔·里胥特·冯·兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初是与风见一样以最年少的年纪出道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到天才之名的他如今已18岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 他不会甘心以普通车手的水平来结束比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位是葵车队的年轻武士新条直辉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有跑车都各就各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿旗挥起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 红灯亮了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见起步漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着 第一个转弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想像以前一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古德利安好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见是今届大赛的焦点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.80,0:04:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还会在这场最终战里向我们展示他惊人的车技吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.30,0:04:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来光靠临阵磨枪的改良仍然是改变不了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可大意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.70,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前有好几次在最后关头输掉比赛的教训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!那么努力也只是跟在他们屁股后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达 变回低速状态2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力煞车尾翼支撑的硬度调整3点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样子车在转弯时 车身振动太大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮胎会支持不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事我知道 快做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开推进器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达打开推进器加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟上海尼尔车后的减低风阻车道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海尼尔把风见压制在后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他无论是以车手身份还是车子设计师身份也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上了这口气不让风见超过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.40,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我认为即使风见这么做也无法接近古德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海尼尔在直线车道一直用推进器加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子阿斯拉达几乎没法追上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且采用旋转驾驶座转弯时车子非常稳定 没有空隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 事态发展成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我连开车都觉得愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然因为这样而落后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.80,0:06:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 车赛的输赢不是光靠车子的性能来决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达 车道外侧 采取低速模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把安定器调到硬度正二度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会导致车转弯时失去平衡 我不赞成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管 照我说的做 追不上的话做什么都没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人!那样的话...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太勉强了!隼人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见隼人和海尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在接合弯道上相撞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.40,0:06:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最不该发生的事发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.10,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风见隼人赌在最后一站\N夺取世界冠军的希望也就到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2019年的世界冠军\N在这瞬间成为杰奇·古德利安的囊中物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对独具特色的双人组合\N合作四年之后终于在今天得到那个荣誉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平日很少笑容的海尼尔脸上...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于逮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了?也不回修理站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是反正又不需要在那里做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不舒服的地方吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.00,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么态度啊 大家都很担心你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是小孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你们担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗? 我们也要撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下我去找你 你要留在房里哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.10,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界冠军  杰奇·古德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 今年是最棒的一年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛伊兹雪铁就像幸运女神一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要向她的设计师法兰兹·海尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和车队的所有工作人员致谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你也越来越会说话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.00,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.80,0:09:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我该问的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得不到冠军就那么不满吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干吗突然说这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人你才是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终战后一直愁眉苦脸的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方别乱说啊 你也不看看场合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 失敬失敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是有意偷听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对明日香说话的口气越来越自大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别乱说啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙说不定是个大男人主义者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是选择兰德尔比较好一点？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你也会有这样说的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么也来这了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.10,0:10:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的东西会吸引人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然明日香小姐在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被吸引来这也是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是老样子啊 兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 那边吵个不停 我受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侥幸也好 那种主角的酒会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想只此一次下不为例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侥幸也好 我也想参加一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.30,0:10:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做主角的高格调派对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远远凌驾普通推进器的超级线性加速器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.80,0:10:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可自由改变转弯时的接地面积的旋转驾驶座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有控制这些功能的最先进计算机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这确实是了不起的构思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他让各方面都达到了完美的境界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到会出现那种车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的时代吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道FICCY将如何对应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论哪个车队都不可能袖手旁观吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会全力开发车子性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们彻底惨败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那已经是过去式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负现在才要开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超高科技时代吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是时候作决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔的时代已经结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.20,0:11:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 但我还不想象你一样抛弃赛车后老朽掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说甚么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然也很介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子果然没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说 是发生什么事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不是那意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相亲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.90,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长他们想请老板别再热衷于赛车的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 他们想到了结婚这个点子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.70,0:12:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新条 今天的颁奖典礼 你应酬一下就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要老待在那里玩 快点回国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美琪也是 从明天起 工作会堆积如山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别给我弄坏了身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这如意算盘是砸定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个赛季看来会很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵车队也会开发新车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位金日子会制造怪物一样的车子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们掌握了知觉的极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零的领域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 车子的极限却可以不断提升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.70,0:13:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟要进步到哪里才满意呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在零的领域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身心早已疲惫不堪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你为什么不放弃赛车?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.30,0:13:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们是很难缠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛的时候我只想赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.82,0:13:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{}富士山脚\N菅生试车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1分20秒43
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把最高纪录缩短了两秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想 幸好你是老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我的位置可就岌岌可危了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是超音速骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别不高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果快不过去年阿斯拉达的时间纪录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么要开发新车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的表现完全不像是久没赛车的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使回到赛车场也没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这么办吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.80,0:14:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若那种医疗技术早一点问世的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就说不定啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在身为试车员也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能驾驶 我就满足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你可别吓我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实现在不是闲谈聊天的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安尼需要再加强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达的新型车身也有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些比是否由我来驾驶更麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.40,0:15:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始我还得去筹备资金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在下午再缩短两秒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那么有干劲 我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是初次驾驶花环吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.70,0:15:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别弄坏它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安尼会哭哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怪就怪这个时候还得痲疹的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达一直待在工厂 欲求不满很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让它尽情飞驰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要让新型车架飞驰起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{}富士冈 葵车队试车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{}司徒加 舒特洛杰试车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.85,0:16:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{}敖德萨 失落之环试车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.80,0:16:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{}维也纳 兰德尔家私人赛车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就完了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有两处地方想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化妆品和...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对...对不起!我稍微走神了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安尼 你累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 要你陪我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.80,0:16:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪录的事一直脱离不了我的脑海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪录?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.70,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我怎么跑也追不上前辈你的纪录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在才开始啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.50,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 阿斯拉达改良后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈你一定会开得更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出人意料的应该是花环反而稍微快对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这次是我第一次驾驶花环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但坦白说 我吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应 马力 每方面都非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想作出行动的剎那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就会立即帮我完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.80,0:17:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花环易于驾驭 是非常好的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是阿斯拉达...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 阿斯拉达也是一部好车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.60,0:17:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 它也有各种麻烦的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.90,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称为阿斯拉达的系统控制着车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.60,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不...花环也一样是由系统控制车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.60,0:18:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达...即使我想作出行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也得需要阿斯拉达同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是花环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会完全服从我的指示去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你明不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我是说阿斯拉达并不是会比较快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.90,0:18:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克蕾雅看起来好辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.70,0:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都过了深夜一时才回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为阿斯拉达的装配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和其它车子截然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.80,0:18:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次和「11」型不同了 要全面改良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以会更辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望阿斯拉达可以快点改良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克蕾雅 休息一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再这样消耗体力会撑不久的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这不是一件能简单结束的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.50,0:19:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还不会差劲到因为这点事就倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人在累倒前都是那样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.30,0:19:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白的说 我想不到你会这么辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 现在终于亲身感受到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫风见广之的男人有多了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此 我这次一定要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.60,0:19:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把阿斯拉达拥有的所有潜力发挥出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你别露出那样的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好歹也是个老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开幕之前是我的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你送到这里就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面就是开幕战的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.10,0:20:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我不说你也知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取胜并不是比赛的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.10,0:20:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也并不打算抱着必败的心情上赛车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代我问候阿斯拉达吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.80,0:20:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟它说「我期待看见改良后的你」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高智能方程式的风见隼人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.10,0:21:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人!为何会在这里!好帅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1分15秒225
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.80,0:21:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈!厉害!接近15秒了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.30,0:21:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板!原来你在场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.70,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈刚才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.80,0:21:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.60,0:21:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.00,0:21:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安尼你不可以只替人高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.00,0:21:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我又落后两秒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板 我有话和你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 我希望克蕾雅也在场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人!你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说请你也让我驾驶花环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.50,0:22:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改良进度这么慢 也许是我不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过五天...不 三天内...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.70,0:22:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克蕾雅你这么努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.20,0:22:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样说虽然很对不起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.60,0:22:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有几个理由这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.10,0:22:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是时间的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.10,0:22:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使阿斯拉达改良了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.60,0:22:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也一定要从头开始进行测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然或许还赶得及开幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.70,0:22:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但时间紧迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.30,0:22:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样我与车子之间的配合也会变得难以调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其这样\N我想不如驾驶现在熟悉的花环去参加比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.30,0:22:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个理由是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.40,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使变得多么新型也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.20,0:22:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对五年前设计的\N阿斯拉达能否对抗现在的高科技存有疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.40,0:22:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人 没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.70,0:23:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何能那么肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使阿斯拉达是当时最先进的系统也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.00,0:23:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但科技进步很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.30,0:23:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达的计算机是早期开发的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.50,0:23:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使车身再怎么改良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.10,0:23:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若计算机相同 极限是不会有什么增加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.50,0:23:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.00,0:23:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其它的车子是截然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.70,0:23:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它还是有可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.70,0:23:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我正在发挥超越阿斯拉达极限的能力」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.10,0:23:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在现今为止的比赛里那样说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.50,0:23:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是克蕾雅你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.10,0:23:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说它还有什么样的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.50,0:23:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.40,0:23:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎说才好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.20,0:23:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那两个理由吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我机缘巧合地成为车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.70,0:23:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是很幸运吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.60,0:23:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能驾驶爸爸的跑车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达是爸爸的遗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.50,0:23:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说也是无可替代的宝物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.40,0:23:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我选择了驾驶爸爸的车子踏上职业车手的路之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想驾驶着父亲的车子结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.20,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯拉达...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我只局限于爸爸的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.40,0:24:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能就看不见自已其它的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.50,0:24:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今后也打算一直身为职业车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.20,0:24:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在赛车场上飞驰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.10,0:24:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那并非要永远驾驶阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.90,0:24:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为...那太勉为其难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.30,0:24:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.20,0:24:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迟些给你答复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.70,0:24:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和克蕾雅详细商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.50,0:24:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.40,0:24:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早就明白了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.30,0:24:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.80,0:24:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我毕竟也是赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.60,0:24:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛伊兹雪铁的高科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.20,0:24:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有隼人自己用花环做出自己的15秒纪录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.80,0:24:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及未改良完成的阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.90,0:24:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综合这些理由...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.70,0:25:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.20,0:25:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼人的要求的确合理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.20,0:25:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你也累坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.70,0:25:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而阿斯拉达还未改良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.30,0:25:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是身为老板的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.00,0:25:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答复刚才就给了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.00,0:25:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.10,0:25:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且隼人今后也并非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.80,0:25:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会一直留在菅生车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.20,0:25:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能了解...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.20,0:25:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.00,0:25:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会马上准备隼人的花环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.10,0:25:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.10,0:25:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
